  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "In some cases, when running several thousands of validators, the beacon node seems to have a significant delay starting block production at first slot of an epoch.\r\n\r\nIt is recognizable by looking at the info log `Creating unsigned block for slot <>`, that is supposed to appear very close to the beginning of the epoch.\r\n\r\nIn some extreme cases the delay is so high that can lead to a late block publishing (after 4s into the slot) causing the block to be reorged out.",
